{"tid":1521751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又話今次和理非行動","createTime":"2019-08-31T10:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T11:28:21.000Z","uid":165028,"like":1,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bf3f45ca2f4754d9e37c929e03c4590237344cbd","tid":1521751,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:40:48.000Z","msg":"結果又俾勇武騎劫左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又封路"},{"pid":"d4f9667423daac8ed9a4d9c48d9ae29612bb3b52","tid":1521751,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:49:32.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山，各自努力，互相支援，希望各位尊重前線，用行動去支援佢地<br />\n<br />\n我係一個出左銅鑼灣既耶撚<br />\n<br />\n前線唔會有時間去上連登，而且上網收得極差，佢地唔會睇到大家對行動既意見，而家唔係不停開新post去屌人或者去比意見既時候，而係：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果你係一個睇緊直播既冷氣軍師</span><br />\n請你地幫手推一啲實際既行動 / 文宣post，並準備好落街接放學既準備<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果你係一個已經係街既非前線</span><br />\n請幫手推同更新一啲現場直擊post，並做好哨兵既角色，隨時支援前線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果你係一個仲睇到呢個post既前線</span><br />\n幫我同前線講聲加油！一定要注意安全，人人都係哨兵，齊上齊落，唔好比任何一個手足落單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力，互相支援</span>"},{"pid":"54f66eeb2e534b88807b1c984f031fadf6986965","tid":1521751,"uid":235277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:50:46.000Z","msg":"不割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6569ab701e30d2e0fe2196e4b9f98fe22bcc1910","tid":1521751,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:51:42.000Z","msg":"我以為勇武今日唔會搞<br />\n今晚買左飛去大會堂聽拉赫曼尼諾夫鋼琴協奏曲架<br />\n而家取消左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8583e9ff2a55207b5f67e468ac4b606d4f17e1e","tid":1521751,"uid":158889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"無撚講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d973c8102d17752478dae22879a0d35d4721d45","tid":1521751,"uid":2230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:53:08.000Z","msg":"今日咪和理非緊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7224d293c93bbb894465a6ade8febcde6491ff30","tid":1521751,"uid":31174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"唔撚洗覆佢 不推文"},{"pid":"b08003000d413fdf3fb00250f2d384a593f87e7b","tid":1521751,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"block"},{"pid":"7843f51cdd97b91577e4e31e07e5957923038f8f","tid":1521751,"uid":156376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:54:20.000Z","msg":"死左膠"},{"pid":"6b5648298faf7925a3abdadff27d85cdf846860f","tid":1521751,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:56:07.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">830 大濫捕 黑警被斬 完全將焦點轉移<br />\n<br />\n提提大家 我地今日出黎目的係<br />\n<br />\n因為5年前831中共就普選設下「提名委員會」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">還我真普選！<br />\n<br />\nBe Water</span></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n大家都係抗爭者 騎咩劫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f543598017bbf5131d953b00ef9a4813eca91810","tid":1521751,"uid":36455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:57:08.000Z","msg":"快啲多謝勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c384ec00282c3852de9cc85e7f3f2247648413e5","tid":1521751,"uid":62811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:58:40.000Z","msg":"唔割"},{"pid":"175c078b30392a7690d5a362da12edcdfe72b73b","tid":1521751,"uid":240374,"like":0,"dislike":